# water-jug*detect*goal*achieved
# If the task is water-jug and there is a jug w/ volum 3 and contents 1,
# then write that the problem has been solved and halt.

sp {water-jug*detect*goal*acheieved
   (state <s> ^name water-jug
              ^jug <j>
              ^desired.jug <dj>)
   (<j> ^volume 3
        ^contents 1)
-->
   (write (crlf) |The problem has been solved.|)
   (halt)}